    "body": "<p><strong style=\"color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Dear Supplier ADM KAP,<\/em><\/strong><\/p><p><em style=\"color: rgb(31, 73, 125); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;<\/em><em style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;<\/em><em style=\"color: rgb(31, 73, 125); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/em><\/p><p><span style=\"color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Berikut kami informasikan Delivery Note ADM KAP.<\/span><\/p><p><br><\/p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 204); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\"Terlampir di attachment sheet dengan Password\" :&nbsp;<\/span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 204); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em><u>adm<\/u><\/em><\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 36, 36); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(31, 73, 125); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Mohon perhatikan dan persiapkan sebelum pengiriman barang sebagai berikut :<\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 73, 125); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><ol><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"><\/span><span style=\"color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Pastikan DN diprint dan dibawa beserta surat jalan supplier.<\/span><\/li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"><\/span><span style=\"color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Pengiriman dapat menyesuaikan tanggal dan jam yang tertera pada DN ( Apabila ada perubahan mohon dikonfirmasikan terlebih dahulu ke team Warehose Consumable ).<\/span><\/li><li